def main():
    x = float(input())
    a = int(x)
    b = int((x - a) * 10)
    print(a, b)

if __name__ == '__main__':
    main()


import sys

def main():
    x = float(sys.stdin.readline())
    a = int(round(x, 0)) # округляем до целого
    b = int(round(x * 10, 0)) - a * 10 # округляем до десятых
    print(a, b)

if __name__ == '__main__':
    main()
